            <title><![CDATA[下午察：开封包公像“申冤”的背后]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2024/03/19/Screenshot6_1.jpg?VersionId=9cuNvfzKcP.4VDX3rrgz7khINaVjlZY6&amp;itok=5OWxsTY7" title="河南开封市一女子跪在开封府大堂前嚎啕大哭的视频日前冲上微博热搜。（互联网）" alt="河南开封市一女子跪在开封府大堂前嚎啕大哭的视频日前冲上微博热搜。（互联网）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2024/03/19/Screenshot6_1.jpg?VersionId=9cuNvfzKcP.4VDX3rrgz7khINaVjlZY6&amp;itok=5OWxsTY7" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div> <figcaption>河南开封市一女子跪在开封府大堂前嚎啕大哭的视频日前冲上微博热搜。（互联网）</figcaption>      <p>影视作品中常常出现古代女子在衙门前含泪鸣冤的场面，在今天的河南开封真实再现。</p><p>河南开封市一女子日前跪在开封府大堂前嚎啕大哭，相关视频上周冲上了微博热搜。</p><p>视频显示，女子跪在开封府大堂前，双手抓扶着护栏，嚎啕大哭，引得不少网民心酸：“这得有多少冤屈啊！”</p><div class="article-microtransaction"><div class="cta-subscribe-new">请<a href="https://subscribe.sph.com.sg/zh/publications-zb/" target="_blank"><span class="link link-underline">订阅</span></a>或<span href="javascript:;" onclick="_mySPHObj.openLogin()" id="paywall-login" class="link link-underline">登录</span>，以继续阅读全文！</div></div><style>
